cast.overview: Shy, straight-A student Ellie is hired by sweet but inarticulate jock Paul, who needs help wooing the most popular girl in school. But their new and unlikely friendship gets tricky when Ellie discovers she has feelings for the same girl.
cast.title: The Half of It

details.biography:
Alexandre is an actor, model, and multidisciplinary artist based in New York City. He holds a B.A. in Theater and Psychology, Cum Laude, from New York University Abu Dhabi, and also studied in New York at the Tisch School of the Arts' Experimental Theater Wing.

Raised in Paris, France, Alexandre is a native speaker of English and French, and holds both U.S. and French Passports. He is a member of SAG-AFTRA, and actively pursues his training at various New York studios.
details.name: Alexandre Bagot
